Information. Biaxin (clarithromycin)." AbbVie US LLC  (2019):|"Product Information. Zithromax (azithromycin)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group  (2021):|"Product Information. E.E.S.-400 Filmtab (erythromycin)." Arbor Pharmaceuticals  (2018):|"Product Information. Priftin (rifapentine)." sanofi-aventis  (2020):', 'DDInter', 0);
